{"author":{"id":"cff9ab1d2ee9741039b2a60d90cca378a5320ba753398f6f3df8d03abcebee1b"},"ops":[{"type":1,"timestamp":1772370937,"nonce":"xyNjtPBdaQW87dzwyvzZJ8uWjco=","title":"Add items list view linked from Verwaltung","message":"There is no dedicated route to browse all items in a department. Users can add articles but there is no articles list view.\n\nThe Verwaltung section should link to an items list at /items (or similar) that shows all items in the current department, similar to how /werkstaetten lists departments.\n\nCurrent state:\n- 'Artikel hinzufügen' (add article) exists but there is no 'Artikel' (articles) list\n- The lending view shows items but only in the context of lending, not for management\n- Verwaltung should link to both the items list and the add article action\n\nProposed structure:\n- /verwaltung links to /items (department-scoped item list)\n- /items shows all ParentItems in the current department\n- From /items, users can add, edit, view, and manage articles\n- Similar pattern to /werkstaetten for departments","files":null}]}